國際輻射單位與度量委員會: ICRU (International Commission on Radiation Units and Measurements)

加熱冷卻率: heat up and cool down rate

燃料元件目標曝露: goal exposure of the fuel elements

混合氧化燃料對一般環境衝擊報告: GESMD (generic environmental statement mixed oxide fuel)

原子或電子的G因數: G factor of atom or electron

地面排洩濾器交叉拉桿閥: floor drain filter cross tie valve

每離子對能量損失: energy loss by per ion pair

控制棒的有效半徑: effective radius of a control rod

缺陷處理報告或偏差處理報告: DDR (defect disposition report or deviation disposition report)

結合構造主要閉路式冷卻水系統: CSECCWS (combination structure essential closed cooling water system)

結合構造閉路冷卻水系統: CSCWS (combination structure closed cooling water system)

計數管的臨界電場: critical field of a counter tube

治療輻射病腎上腺素: cortisone in treatment of radiation illness
